title: Into The Woods (feat. Greg Fitzsimmons)
description:
Greg Fitzsimmons joins Big Jay Oakerson & Dan Soder on The Bonfire and tells the gang about writing a book that reads like his diary and a story of a time he was planning on experimenting in the woods and then second guessed himself when faced with the realty of the situation.
